body:
This mod fixes a few issues present in older versions of The Twilight Forest, these being:
- Door items not having textures, causing them to be rendered as pink and black squares;
- The transwood trapdoor using the twilight oak trapdoor texture;
- Missing english localization names for certain blocks/entities.

Fixed textures and models taken from this [pull request by xemnes](https://github.com/TeamTwilight/twilightforest/pull/1225).
